<H2 id="brief-synopsis" id="toc-hId-929701130">Brief synopsis</H2><BR />
In the previous episode (Ep.12) we looked at a simple CSV filter utility. In this episode we improve it by giving it the ability to read from STDIN and write to STDOUT so it plays nicely in pipeline contexts. Then we‚Äôll be ready to use it to finalise our data for our CAP based ‚ÄúNorthbreeze‚Äù service.<BR />
